[SN]TITLE[SN]
Jimmy Savile report: Full text

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An inquiry by former head of Sky News Nick Pollard into the way Newsnight shelved an investigation into sexual abuse by Jimmy Savile has concluded there was no cover-up, but there were management failings.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The report said the decision to drop the original investigation was flawed but it was not done to protect the Savile tribute programmes which were broadcast late last year.
